Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Incredible Unit Offering High End Finishes and Water Views from a Private Deck. This Spacious 2 bed 2 bath has it all Including a Master Suite with a Full Bathroom, Glass Shower and Walk In Closet, the Oversized Living Room features a Gas Fireplace and opens to a Luxurious Kitchen, Chefs Range and a Massive Island for Entertaining Guests. Laundry In Unit. All of this in Perhaps the Best Location in the City, Just Steps to the Beach and Castle Island! Video Tour Available upon Request.
